## 🏗️ Structural & Civil Considerations
* **Battery Weight Loading:** High-density battery racks require reinforced floor slabs (coordinated with Project 2).
* **Thermal Dissipation:** UPS and Battery rooms require dedicated cooling ($Q_{ups} = \sim 4\%$ of total power capacity).
* **Containment:** Battery rooms designed with acid-resistant flooring and hydrogen gas monitoring/ventilation.

